Password Toggle App
• Create a React application that allows users to show and hide 
their password using a button.
• The application should:
• Display a password input field 
• Hide the password initially 
• Show the password when the user clicks the “Show Password” 
button 
• Hide the password again when the user clicks “Hide Password” 
• Change the button text dynamically based on the current state
Login Logout Toggle App
• Create a React application that displays different 
components based on the login status of the user.
• The application should:
• Show a “Login” button initially 
• Display the Home component when the user is logged 
out 
• Display the Profile component when the user logs in 
• Change the button text from “Login” to “Logout” 
dynamically 
• Toggle between components using conditional rendering
